OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FA campaigner from Northern Ireland is
OL,7,Fcalling on Crown Dependencies to
OL,8,Fconsider becoming test beds for
OL,9,Flegalising recreational cannabis use.
OL,11,FCharlotte Caldwell successfully
OL,12,Flobbied the UK government to allow her
OL,13,Fdisabled son the right to a medicinal
OL,14,Fcannabis prescription.
OL,16,FShe says she's received support from
OL,17,FChannel Island governments for the
OL,18,Fidea of a cannabis pilot scheme, and
OL,19,Fhas been meeting Jersey's Health
OL,20,FMinister, Deputy Tom Binet, for the
OL,21,Flast three years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FShe told ITV Channel: "I'm not asking
OL,7,Fthem to commit - I'm asking them to
OL,8,Flearn."
OL,10,FMs Caldwell says she's lobbying all
OL,11,Fthe devolved governments, but has
OL,12,Freceived the most backing from the
OL,13,FCrown Dependencies and believes this
OL,14,Fmay be because the governments are
OL,15,Fable to make their own laws related to
OL,16,Fdrug policy.
OL,18,FThe campaigner continued: "It can be
OL,19,Fdone through public health, through
OL,20,Fthe health ministers in the British
OL,21,FCrown Dependencies and across the UK.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,F"There is an appetite there and where
OL,7,Fthere is a will, there's a way."
OL,9,FThe proposed pilot scheme would
OL,10,Finvolve volunteers over the age of 21,
OL,11,Fwho would be given up to 40 grams of
OL,12,Fcannabis per month.
OL,14,FThey would also need to produce a
OL,15,Fletter from their medical professional
OL,16,Fconfirming they do not have a history
OL,17,Fof any mental health conditions, and
OL,18,Fundergo health monotoring.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FIn a similar pilot scheme in
OL,7,FSwitzerland last year, more than
OL,8,F10,000 adults took part in the Swiss
OL,9,Fpublic health trial which found it
OL,10,Fprogressed "without "any notable
OL,11,Fincidents or negative effects on
OL,12,Fhealth or public order".
OL,14,FCannabis is a relatively new industry
OL,15,Fin Jersey. It was legalised for
OL,16,Fmedicinal use in 2018 and since then
OL,17,Fit's become a lucrative industry.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
