PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FNeel Sahai, CEO of Green Island
OL,7,FGrowers, a Jersey-based cultivator and
OL,8,Fmanufacturer of medicinal cannabis,
OL,9,Ftold ITV Channel that the pilot scheme
OL,10,Fis "the most suitable avenue for the
OL,11,Fgovernment to go down".
OL,13,F"We've seen in recreational pilot
OL,14,Fprojects in progressive countries that
OL,15,Fthe war on drugs and prohibition isn't
OL,16,Fworking. It's feeding criminal
OL,17,Fenterprise, and people are still using
OL,18,Fcannabis."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FHe adds that a well-regulated project
OL,7,Fand trial that gathers data ensures
OL,8,Fthe product "is safe for use", as well
OL,9,Fas being controlled and within a
OL,10,Fstrict time limit.
OL,12,FWhile there is some support, there's
OL,13,Falso concern that opening the door to
OL,14,Fwider use could put some at risk.
OL,16,F"If the results aren't what you want,
OL,17,Fyou can reverse out of it," he says.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FMr Sahai continues that the pilot
OL,7,Fproject satisfies a "negotiated middle
OL,8,Fground" between those that want
OL,9,Fcannabis in society and those that
OL,10,Fdon't.
OL,12,F"People who are concerned can feel
OL,13,Fcomfort in the fact that it's
OL,14,Fcontrollable, with registered
OL,15,Fparticipants".
OL,17,FHe describes it as a "stepping stone"
OL,18,Fto wider legalisation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1778073067
OL,3,CCampaigner calls on Crown Dependencies
OL,4,Cto become cannabis test beds
OL,6,FThe cannabis manufacturer added that
OL,7,Fhe doesn't think the UK government "is
OL,8,Ftrying to angle Jersey as a test bed",
OL,9,Fbut it's instead being "driven by a
OL,10,Fspecific need on the island".
OL,12,FHowever, it will be up to Jersey's
OL,13,Fpoliticians to sign-off on any
OL,14,Fproposals, which may take some time.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
